                projects, add tasks, set deadlines, and never miss a thing with smart reminders and notifications.
                Perfect for students, teams, and professionals!</p>
            <ul class="mb-8 space-y-3">
                <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-blue-500 mr-2">&#10003;</span> Create & manage unlimited
                    projects</li>
                <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-blue-500 mr-2">&#10003;</span> Add tasks to each project
                    with priorities & deadlines</li>
                <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-blue-500 mr-2">&#10003;</span> Get daily email reminders
                    for upcoming deadlines</li>
                <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-blue-500 mr-2">&#10003;</span> Secure login/signup with
                    OTP verification</li>
                <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-blue-500 mr-2">&#10003;</span> Mark tasks & projects as
